{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_05_01",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 1話 ゲストにはあの人を",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoirが星見プロに入所した直後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After LizNoir transfered into Hoshimi Production",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 3.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 3.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワのステージ、凄く盛り上がってますね\n私の出番ももうすぐ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir's stage is really getting hyped up.\nMy turn is coming up soon…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.9914057415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.1580724081
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "緊張はしてるみたいだけど、いい顔をしてるな\nその様子なら大丈夫そうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem nervous‚ but you have a confident look.\nWith that attitude‚ I'm sure you'll be fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.5247390748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "はい。莉央さんと歌うのは緊張しますけど……\nそれ以上に凄く頼もしくて、楽しみなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Singing with Rio-san makes me nervous…\nBut more than that‚ I find it reassuring and exciting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.7580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.5914057415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……お姉ちゃん、見てくれてるかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I wonder if my big sister is watching.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5914057415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――これよりしばらく前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A long time ago",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.7914057415
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.7914057415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "仕事の合間にまで打ち合わせさせて悪いな、琴乃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for having a meeting even during your work‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.8580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、月ストのアルバムを作らせてもらえるんですから\nこれくらい平気です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's fine. I'm being allowed to work on Moon Tempest's album‚ so\nI'm okay with this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.9580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.9247390748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "それで……なんですけど。アルバムでどんなことが\nしたいか、みんなから意見をもらってきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… Well‚ I've gathered opinions from everyone about what they want\nto do with the album.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "まずは、すずの案で各曲の月スト五人バージョンと\nすずのソロバージョンを入れたい……だそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First‚ according to Suzu's suggestion‚ she wants to include versions of\neach song with all five members of Moon Tempest‚ as well as a solo version",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0914057415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.7247390748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "可能なら、すずのソロはジャズバージョンなど\nアレンジを加えたものも収録したいそうで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "for Suzu…and if possible‚ for Suzu's solo‚\nshe'd like to add arrangements like a jazz version…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.0914057415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.3580724081
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "一発目から頭が痛くなるな……\nとりあえず、他のみんなのも一通り聞くよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My head hurts right from the start…\nAnyway‚ I'll listen to what the others have to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.4247390748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣は曲順をあみだくじで決めたいそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei wants to decide the song order with a draw.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.8580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.6247390748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "……くじの番号は、さとみさんの家の猫が\nふみふみしたものを選んだらどうかな、と",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…She suggested using numbers from the lottery drawn by Satomi-san's cat\nafter it had stepped on them. What do you think about that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.2247390748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "猫がふみふみか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The cat stepping on the numbers‚ huh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.0580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.2247390748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……猫がふみふみ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… the cat stepping on the numbers…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2247390748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.5580724081
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "渚は歌詞カードに曲に対する想いを\n書き込んでみたらどうかと言っていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa suggested that maybe she could write down her feelings about each song\non the lyric card. And for the album‚ she thought about adding photos taken",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.5580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "後は制作時の写真を載せたりするのも楽しそう\nとのことで、これは私も賛成です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "during the production. It sounds fun‚\nso I'm on board with that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.5580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.4247390748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "レッスン風景をメンバーが撮ることは\nよくありますから、素材は困らないかなと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since the members often take pictures of each other during lessons‚\nwe shouldn't have trouble with material.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.5247390748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、月ストメンバーの日常を知ることも\n出来て良さそうだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ it seems like a good idea to get to know Moon Tempest members' daily lives.\nThat makes sense.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.1247390748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.9580724081
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "沙季は、曲単位で楽しむ人が多いという最近の風潮を\n考慮したアルバムを作りたいと言っていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki mentioned that lately many people enjoy songs on a per-track basis‚\nso she wants to create an album that considers this trend.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.2914057415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "歌詞カードの曲間に詩を添えたり、物語性を感じる\n曲順にしてみる……という案を出してくれました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She suggested adding poems between the lyrics on the lyric card‚ and\narranging the songs in a way that creates a sense of narrative.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.8580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.6914057415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "アルバムを一つの大きな作品として捉えてもらう\nという狙いは私も賛成です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I agree with her intention to\nhave the album seen as one big piece of work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.9580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくのアルバムですから、一曲一曲よりも\n流れで聞いてもらいたいなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since it's a special album‚ I hope people will listen to it as a whole\nrather than just focusing on individual tracks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.6247390748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.8914057415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……渚と沙季の意見はちゃんとしてるな\nいや、すずと芽衣がちゃんとしてない訳ではないんだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Nagisa and Saki's opinions are well thought out.\nWell‚ it's not that Suzu and Mei's opinions aren't thought out either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.3247390748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんとした意見もそうでない意見も\n遠慮なく言い合えるのは凄くいいと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it's great that everyone can express both well-thought and unconventional\nopinions without hesitation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.5247390748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.0247390748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "確かにな。……っと、そろそろ次の仕事の時間だな\n続きは夜でいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Definitely… Well‚ it's almost time for your next work.\nCan we continue this tonight?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.7580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_night",
      "startTime": 169.1247390748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "さて、アルバム制作の話の続きだが……\n琴乃はどんなアルバムにしたいんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ continuing the discussion about the album…\nWhat kind of album do you want‚ Kotono?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.9580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんの曲をカバーしたいなって思ってました\nみんなに提案したら大賛成してもらえて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was thinking about covering my sister's songs.\nWhen I proposed the idea‚ everyone was on board…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.6914057415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのメンバーにもゲスト出演してもらったら\nどうかっていう話になったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and we even discussed having members from Hoshimi Pro.\nas guest performers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.3247390748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn021.m4a",
      "text": "お互いの曲をカバーしあったら……なんて話まで\n出たんですけど、さすがに収拾がつかなくなりそうで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We talked about covering each other's songs…\nbut things got a bit out of hand‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.0247390748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn022.m4a",
      "text": "それで結局、ゲスト出演してもらうなら、お姉ちゃんの\n曲をカバーしてもらうという話でまとまりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so we eventually settled on covering\nher songs only‚ if we have guest appearances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.4914057415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それは良さそうだな。みんなの違った一面が見れそうだ\nゲスト出演の具体案はあるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That sounds like a good idea. It could reveal different sides of everyone.\nDo you have any specific ideas for the guest performers?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.7914057415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn023.m4a",
      "text": "私は……リズノワにカバーしてもらいたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… I'd like LizNoir to do a cover.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.2914057415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワか……莉央さんが承諾するかどうか不安だな\nそれじゃあ、まずは俺から莉央さんに話を通すよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir‚ huh… I'm not sure if Rio-san will agree to that.\nAlright then‚ I'll talk to Rio-san about it first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.8914057415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn024.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……これは私が希望したことなので\n私から莉央さんにお願いさせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… this is something I wanted‚\nso please let me be the one to ask Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 228.4914057415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "え。まぁ、琴乃がそう言うなら……。分かってるとは\n思うけど、先輩相手なんだから失礼はないようにな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Well‚ if you're saying that‚ I understand.\nBut remember‚ you're dealing with a senpai‚ so be polite‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.2580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn025.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです、ありがとうございます\n明日さっそく行ってみます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ thank you very much.\nI'll go talk to her tomorrow!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.6247390748,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6066.666666700002,
          "startTime": 249.6914057415
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn026.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、お疲れ様でした。失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ good work today. Excuse me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.9914057415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃……なんだかいつも以上に押しが強かったな\nどうしたんだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono… You seemed more assertive than usual.\nI wonder what's gotten into her?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.2914057415,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
